allAlerts: FROM NrAiIncident SELECT timestamp, title, priority, incidentLink WHERE entity.name = '210135-Partner Ready Portal (PRP)-Production' AND event = 'open' SINCE 1 DAYS AGO
uniqueAlerts: FROM NrAiIncident SELECT uniques(title) WHERE entity.name = '210135-Partner Ready Portal (PRP)-Production' AND event = 'open' SINCE 1 DAYS AGO
